title: Match History broken

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: the match history website is not working for me. I checked the EUW one, that one works fine, but NA is not.

replies.body: Mine doesn't work on EUW and NA  but works on EUNE -.-"

There's a known issue with the match history page that causes it to not load for certain people. It's something we're looking into. In the meantime, I recommend trying a quick [clear of your browser's cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or trying a different web browser to see if anything changes.

Let me know if you have any questions.
